Teach for America is an organization
that provides teachers to underserved,

6
00:00:23.850 --> 00:00:26.190
underprivileged school
districts around the country.

7
00:00:26.190 --> 00:00:30.150
They do this by hiring students straight
out of college and training them and

8
00:00:30.150 --> 00:00:32.710
then putting them into these schools for
a couple of years.

9
00:00:32.710 --> 00:00:34.900
And they've been doing this for
